LOOP AT x_konv INTO wa_konv WHERE ( NOT kbetr IS INITIAL ) AND KPOSN+1(5) EQ WA_EKPO-EBELP.
IF wa_konv-kschl = 'P000' OR wa_konv-kschl = 'P001' OR wa_konv-kschl = 'PB00' OR wa_konv-kschl = 'PBXX'.

MODIFY i_cond FROM wa_cond TRANSPORTING amt WHERE kschl = wa_konv-kschl .
LOOP AT x_komv INTO wa_komv WHERE ( NOT kbetr IS INITIAL ) AND ( kschl NE 'BASB' ) AND KPOSN+1(5) EQ WA_EKPO-EBELP.
READ TABLE i_cond INTO wa_cond WITH KEY kschl = wa_komv-kschl.
MODIFY i_cond FROM wa_cond TRANSPORTING amt WHERE kschl = wa_komv-kschl .
